{{Han etym}}
{{Han simp|纍|f=畾|t=田}}.

Folk etymology considers this character as an ideographic compound representing the [[tiredness]] after work. In ancient China, men were working in the field ({{zh-l|*田}}) while women sewed ({{zh-l|*糸}}).

